  - Backend: use `ActivityLogModel` status-change events as source data
  - Analytics: lead time, cycle time, time in review, blocked time, reopened count
  - API: workspace, project, sprint, task, and assignee metrics

- [ ] Add sprint health metrics
  - Analytics: velocity, carryover tasks, scope added after sprint start, completion ratio
  - API: sprint burndown data using story points and status history
  - API: compare current sprint against historical average velocity

- [ ] Add engineering dashboard endpoints
  - API: `GET /analytics/workspace/:workspaceId/engineering`
  - API: `GET /analytics/project/:projectId/workspace/:workspaceId/engineering`
  - Include: throughput, blocked items, overdue review, active PRs, deployment health

