  - Fields: reviewers, status, requiredApprovals, approvedBy, rejectedBy, comments
  - Rules: optionally block moving tasks to done until approvals pass

- [ ] Add Definition of Done checklists
  - Backend: add reusable checklist templates per workspace/project/task type
